@kennytilton when you go to "receive" in Status you should be able to copy the address from there. 

Once on the "receive" screen click the send in the top right corner and "copy" this will copy your wallet address that you can paste here or send an email to me with! 

Thanks.

0x30c71ebccd5cfe19d3da3fd0f02975d87218fbb6
Ok, that works. Thanks for the support. :)

